What is SmashBomb?

Epicenter: Garbage in, Data out
Text input, no submit button

Min 6 characters
Max?

Live search after min characters? Or
Once the use has started smashing listen for them to stop for 1 second and submit request.

Time limit on smashing once started.
Fuse on bomb started for 5 seconds.

Validation:
Not a word (requires a set of dictionaries)
Limit repetition of characters

Storage:
UTF-8 Strings
Couchdb? Mongodb?

Results:
Length of smash
Time stamp of each keystroke
Keyboard detection?
Typing speed
Related smashes by similar characters? Related content?

Reports/stats:
Reports on data collected.


PANIC ROOM
Anonymous user chat log of real-time smashbombs. 